    SELECT [t1].[DateCreated], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [x.ProductCategory.Products0].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [Products] AS [x.ProductCategory.Products0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [x2].[DateCreated], [x2].[Id], [x.ProductCategory2].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [Products] AS [x2]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.ProductCategory2] ON [x2].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory2].[Id]
        WHERE [x2].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x2].[DateCreated] DESC, [x2].[Id], [x.ProductCategory2].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1] ON [x.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t1].[Id0]
) AS [t2] ON [x.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t2].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t2].[DateCreated] DESC, [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id1]" (0723d8ff)

            WHERE (((DATEPART(year, [n3].[DateCreated]) >= @__fromDate_Year_0) AND (DATEPART(month, [n3].[DateCreated]) >= @__fromDate_Month_1)) AND (DATEPART(day, [n3].[DateCreated]) >= @__fromDate_Day_2)) AND (((DATEPART(year, [n3].[DateCreated]) <= @__toDate_Year_3) AND (DATEPART(month, [n3].[DateCreated]) <= @__toDate_Month_4)) AND (DATEPART(day, [n3].[DateCreated]) <= @__toDate_Day_5))
            ORDER BY [n3].[DateCreated] DESC, [n3].[Id]
            OFFSET @__p_6 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_7 ROWS ONLY
        ) AS [t4] ON [n.BillDetails2].[BillId] = [t4].[Id]
    ) AS [t5] ON [dto.Product.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t5].[Id1]
) AS [t6] ON [dto.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t6].[Id2]

        FROM [Functions] AS [f]
        INNER JOIN [Permissions] AS [p] ON [f].[Id] = [p].[FunctionId]
        INNER JOIN [AppRoles] AS [r] ON [p].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
        WHERE ([r].[Name] IN (N'Admin') AND ([f].[Id] = @__functionId_1)) AND ([p].[CanDelete] = 1))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END" (0723d8ff)
